  "title": "Indian Cook",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>**Key Responsibilities:**</p>\n<p>- Preparing and cooking a variety of Indian dishes, including vegetarian and non-vegetarian options.</p>\n<p>- Following recipes and adjusting spices and ingredients to meet customer preferences.</p>\n<p>- Managing food prep, including chopping, marinating, and assembling ingredients.</p>\n<p>- Maintaining cleanliness and sanitation of the kitchen and work area.</p>\n<p>- Ensuring proper storage of ingredients and leftovers.</p>\n<p>- Monitoring cooking times and temperatures to ensure food safety.</p>\n<p>- Collaborating with kitchen staff to ensure timely service.</p>\n<p>- Ordering and managing inventory of ingredients and supplies.</p>\n<p>- Adhering to health and safety regulations and standards.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>**Qualifications:**</p>\n<p>- Proven experience in Indian cuisine cooking.</p>\n<p>- Knowledge of Indian spices, herbs, and cooking techniques.</p>\n<p>- Ability to work efficiently in a fast-paced environment.</p>\n<p>- Good understanding of food safety and hygiene standards.</p>\n<p>- Culinary training or certification is a plus.</p>\n<p>- Ability to adapt recipes to accommodate dietary restrictions or preferences.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>**Working Conditions:**</p>\n<p>- Working hours may include evenings, weekends, and holidays.</p>\n<p>- Standing for long periods in a hot and busy kitchen.</p>\n<p>- Ability to handle multiple tasks simultaneously.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
